{"tid":1699332,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【周同學RIP】今日TVB洗版任務 - 蝗祖藍公司偽人代言嘅 \"OTO\"","createTime":"2019-11-08T03:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T13:06:10.000Z","uid":267969,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"070f307b174743483a94331c121b5e024912a43b","tid":1699332,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">【任務一：簽聯署】</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>11月9日截止</strong></span>，81%完成，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只欠 19,830人聯署</span></strong>，最後衝刺❗️<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請求美國請將電視廣播有限公司（TVB）高層納入《香港人權及民主法案》的制裁名單：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32jy4fj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32jy4fj&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f8c790d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32jy4fj</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【二】</strong></span><br />\n為周梓樂默哀 (一路打字一路眼濕忍住)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【任務三：抵制CCTVB 每日任務】</span></strong><br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n <br />\n是日精選@8 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>OTO</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/OTOHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOTOHK%2F&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=31ea0beb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/OTOHK/</a></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※記得用留言template</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/73282813_492515548271966_5427154060006391808_o.png?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_eui2=AeFmi_oOqdcFKJrdkNU-NWGQ67IRldMnBgCLFlU1jSflvzE6S5nvIDtn1Y7901k9sfyLx5xkNMzztu019pARUau-TpdrdSXYA_DfpVKjp0z5hQ&amp;_nc_oc=AQkSupkhW28ly2JiE3NRA5Vz60LXeIdMgX1HtlGXNFAIaQ6N8t4EWdQXyc0Wuwj-AvM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=01f2c119f193d1502fa34b178213b64e&amp;oe=5E4DCB0B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F73282813_492515548271966_5427154060006391808_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_eui2%3DAeFmi_oOqdcFKJrdkNU-NWGQ67IRldMnBgCLFlU1jSflvzE6S5nvIDtn1Y7901k9sfyLx5xkNMzztu019pARUau-TpdrdSXYA_DfpVKjp0z5hQ%26_nc_oc%3DAQkSupkhW28ly2JiE3NRA5Vz60LXeIdMgX1HtlGXNFAIaQ6N8t4EWdQXyc0Wuwj-AvM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D01f2c119f193d1502fa34b178213b64e%26oe%3D5E4DCB0B&h=14c4b0d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等睇連登仔表演：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SatTL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SatTL0.jpg&h=14e6d0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>講下臭屎</strong></span><br />\n2005年一個婦人喺OTO嘅專櫃度試用足部按摩機時遇到機件故障，試用十幾分鐘後<span style=\"color: red;\">無法將腳拔出</span>，最後要消防員拆散按摩機將其腳拔出先可以脫險！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本來咁多年前嘅事都冇人記得</span>，但係你哋喺TVB劇集大賣植入廣告，就要挖返件事去證明產品有幾&ldquo;安全&rdquo;！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2015年OTO被中資騰邦控股收購後就<span style=\"color: red;\">搵共狗蝗祖藍旗下偽人代言</span>，蝗生間公司邵氏有股份，即係CCTVB間接分到代言費。快啲換咗個代言人啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家用呢幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被按摩器夾腳好痛架！<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/q3G8S8O.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3G8S8O.jpg&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=01199535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/q3G8S8O.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3G8S8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3G8S8O.jpg&h=79481cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又可以用呢幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個page唔可以upload相做留言，可以留呢條link代替<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/SS8qitc.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSS8qitc.jpg&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=e6af1f93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/SS8qitc.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SS8qitc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSS8qitc.jpg&h=49c4d6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3103059829720421&amp;id=199203203439446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3103059829720421%26id%3D199203203439446&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f90875b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3103059829720421&amp;id=199203203439446</a><br />\n呢個活動請咗<span style=\"color: red;\">岑麗香</span>做嘉賓，快啲㩒入去呢個Post留言同派嬲話俾主辦機構知唔想見到蝗祖藍嘅偽人啦！<br />\n齊齊反對主辦機構間接科水俾蝗祖藍同CCTVB！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=78c81971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>  <br />\n －－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=0b117cbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb <br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=4f699afa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 抵制綜合組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=38956be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb</a><br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=1f12ad69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a>"},{"pid":"29c38d317ba771d84a9e9dd6a71e4b526d260276","tid":1699332,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a1a97017ebd56852584d7c82e93ed9e76e583b","tid":1699332,"uid":262379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:57:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1fdaa9d1e18327b1c863d7f71a30725c8c3a7fc","tid":1699332,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc